    text: "\n# Occurrences\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **010.13.03.01.01** -- Identify an occurrence as being either an accident,\n    incident or serious incident in Regulation (EU) No 996/2010 of the European\n    Parliament and of the Council of 20 October 2010 on the investigation and\n    prevention of accidents and incidents in civil aviation.\n2.  **010.13.03.01.02** -- Describe the relationship between Regulation (EU) No\n    996/2010 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 20 October 2010 on\n    the investigation and prevention of accidents and incidents in civil aviation\n    and Regulation (EU) No 376/2014 of the European Parliament and of the Council\n    of 3 April 2014 on the reporting, analysis and follow-up of occurrences in\n    civil aviation.\n3.  **010.13.03.01.03** -- State the subject matter and scope of Regulation (EU)\n    No 376/2014.\n4.  **010.13.03.01.04** -- Identify occurrences that must be reported.\n5.  **010.13.03.01.05** -- Identify occurrences that should be voluntarily\n    reported.\n6.  **010.13.03.01.06** -- Describe how information from occurrences is\n    collected, stored and analysed.\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 010.13.03.01.01 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 010.13.03.01.02 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 010.13.03.01.03 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 010.13.03.01.04 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 010.13.03.01.05 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 010.13.03.01.06 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n",
