    text: '\n# Engine handling\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **021.10.10.02.01** -- State the correct procedures for setting the engine\n    controls when increasing or decreasing power.\n2.  **021.10.10.02.02** -- Define the following terms: take-off power; maximum\n    continuous power.\n3.  **021.10.10.02.03** -- Describe the start problems associated with extreme\n    cold weather.\n4.  **021.10.10.02.04** -- Describe the principal difference between a\n    full-authority digital engine control (FADEC) system-controlled engine and\n    traditional manual engine controls.\n5.  **021.10.10.02.05** -- Describe the engine controls available on the flight\n    deck for a FADEC-controlled engine.\n6.  **021.10.10.02.06** -- Explain that the FADEC has full authority of the\n    control of all engine parameters ensuring efficient and correct running of\n    the engine, including protection in the event of failure.\n7.  **021.10.10.02.07** -- Explain the need for FADEC redundancy with regard to\n    power supply and data input and output.\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 021.10.10.02.01 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 021.10.10.02.02 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 021.10.10.02.03 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 021.10.10.02.04 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 021.10.10.02.05 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 021.10.10.02.06 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 021.10.10.02.07 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n\n### FADEC\n\nControls:\n\n- Engine Mode selector -> Usually **normal** and **start**.\n\n<Question id="Y4F6LU4LJ7" lo="021.10.10.02.05">\n  <Text variant="oneCorrect">\n    What engine controls are available on the flight deck for a FADEC-controlled\n    engine\n  </Text>\n\n{" "}\n<Option correct>\n  A FADEC computer, an engine mode selector, engine master selectors, and power\n  levers providing digital inputs.\n</Option>\n\n  <Option>A FADEC computer</Option>\n  <Option>A FADEC computer and a an autothrust system</Option>\n  <Option>A FADEC computer and power levers providing digital inputs.</Option>\n</Question>\n',
