    text: "\n# Aircraft performance database\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **022.11.02.02.01** -- Explain the purpose of, and describe the typical\n    content of, the aircraft performance database.\n2.  **022.11.02.02.02** -- Explain the importance of verifying that the aircraft\n    performance database is based on the correct data, such as engine type and\n    aircraft variant.\n3.  **022.11.02.02.03** -- Explain that the contents of the aircraft performance\n    database cannot be modified by the pilot.\n4.  **022.11.02.02.04** -- Explain the purpose of performance factor and how it\n    influences the calculations.\n5.  **022.11.02.02.05** -- Explain the purpose of cost index (CI) and how it\n    influences the calculations.\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 022.11.02.02.01 | X       |        | X          | X           |        | X   |         |\n| 022.11.02.02.02 | X       |        | X          | X           |        | X   |         |\n| 022.11.02.02.03 | X       |        | X          | X           |        | X   |         |\n| 022.11.02.02.04 | X       |        | X          | X           |        | X   |         |\n| 022.11.02.02.05 | X       |        |            |             |        |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n",
