    id: "032.01.01.01",
    text: "\n# Applicability of airworthiness requirements of CS-23 and CS-25\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **032.01.01.01.01** -- Describe the application of certification\n    specification (CSs) with regard to the different kinds of aeroplanes.\n2.  **032.01.01.01.02** -- Describe the general differences between aeroplanes\n    certified according to CS-23 and CS-25.\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 032.01.01.01.01 | X       | X      |            |             |        |     |         |\n| 032.01.01.01.02 | X       |        |            |             |        |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n",
