    id: "032.04.06.01",
    text: "\n# Approach requirements\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **032.04.06.01.01** -- Describe the CS-25 requirements for the approach climb\n    (one-engine-inoprative).\n2.  **032.04.06.01.02** -- Describe the CS-25 requirements for the landing climb.\n3.  **032.04.06.01.03** -- Explain the effect of temperature and pressure\n    altitude on approach and landing-climb performance.\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 032.04.06.01.01 | X       |        |            |             |        |     |         |\n| 032.04.06.01.02 | X       |        |            |             |        |     |         |\n| 032.04.06.01.03 | X       |        |            |             |        |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n",
