    text: "\n# Triangle of velocities (TOV)\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 061.01.06.01.01 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 061.01.06.02.01 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n\n1.  **061.01.06.01.01** -- Draw and correctly label the TOV.\n2.  **061.01.06.02.01** -- Resolve the TOV for: heading and GS (with mechanical\n    computer and MDR); WV (with mechanical computer); and track and GS (with\n    mechanical computer and MDR.\n\n## Summary\n",
