    text: '\n# Dead reckoning (DR)\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **061.01.07.01.01** -- Determine a DR position.\n2.  **061.01.07.01.02** -- Evaluate the difference between a DR and a fix\n    position.\n3.  **061.01.07.01.03** -- Define "speed factor" (SF). Speed divided by 60, used\n    for mental flight-path calculations.\n4.  **061.01.07.01.04** -- Calculate wind correction angle (WCA) using the\n    formula: WCA = XWC (crosswind component)/SF\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 061.01.07.01.01 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 061.01.07.01.02 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 061.01.07.01.03 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n| 061.01.07.01.04 | X       | X      | X          | X           | X      |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n',
