    text: "\n# Basics of airflow\n\n## Learning Objectives\n\n1.  **081.01.01.02.01** -- Describe steady and unsteady airflow.\n2.  **081.01.01.02.02** -- Explain the concept of a streamline and a stream tube.\n3.  **081.01.01.02.03** -- Describe and explain airflow through a stream tube.\n4.  **081.01.01.02.04** -- Explain the difference between two- and\n    three-dimensional airflow.\n\n|                 | ATPL(A) | CPL(A) | ATPL(H)/IR | ATPL(H)/VFR | CPL(H) | IR  | CBIR(A) |\n| --------------- | ------- | ------ | ---------- | ----------- | ------ | --- | ------- |\n| 081.01.01.02.01 | X       | X      |            |             |        |     |         |\n| 081.01.01.02.02 | X       | X      |            |             |        |     |         |\n| 081.01.01.02.03 | X       | X      |            |             |        |     |         |\n| 081.01.01.02.04 | X       | X      |            |             |        |     |         |\n\n## Summary\n",
